C7yPtTk0tHjUmXFDeaCDfbI0vq_MrL3SIz5--croGuv4kf9e2TQU7Xwp3JMIce3-SbMHQVN7ynkTV3YAab1_G79ZGafJk83YADEJ3kFOK91j5e1Q_HVP54kJI0IxETVsVcGmh-S56AkE9KM10Jpb5_0eG0FZhpnSDe5Kwl01ORTHfDs3EVZ-kZfOUAxbJdNze4juyRLQHAdPTdE4LxxhgoXX8J6FxBtwRCv0/xq23JuJKtcKP4NMGjz4gcrPQP8wOIfOW/9"&gt;以色列对伊朗核设施的袭击&lt;/a&gt;导致股票在周五下跌，但国内动荡似乎并没有加以利用。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;彭博经济学的经济学家尼克·霍尔马克（Nick Hallmark）说：“从外部（这是一种违反直觉）。”政治上的不稳定似乎是一种会震惊投资者和凹陷经济体的事情，但是本周，Hallmark发表了一项分析（ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/QWMx49-blplsQRV_35viGEWqt1-8bDBZfmUGLugep0Klrw0Ug-L6PN8lebMVYRHaLvd0qSs6pBE276-epQ7e16s0Hc1-YvThpSNWAWbBhkzT9WKSperkhttuXkK3-YjNezer5kLkmgt4T356tZuBAC0IlSBjtjb6YJrp_TwKKCgf-V2wHlScgBrGLUkMRFEoXqarvsFS-ezl6lVxhepy-wPLAxY9MPgYRVU2kfdcZuymJIHABx-QP86xS2Mw6TxyzYcKSbhYVOsDlb9qNISUcXUmx-w72UfAeljkX1MyRHtPP4-t2GLmyOxDAYb8LhPpfAY9_lLWCr8-0lwM0HHevecr_qknLELrvX8VPZDue0Pt9eOM2n-UDKFXhKxfX34wkrDp3qcL86dFud0dt7pJyNAhGT--KlZbXS1q8N4JHE2EDUz_Ib7I4k7r0HUjDZjxsWOkOvAUkxVdZlC1oGfNWAdawkr1w9Lryv-buEoqw_oCK_thHlfdLccp4xHZLxsm98r2yWCuuZPeO9yvgc4vAs-dbIMKqX_Tt0GiuGQDj38djMlwAFccDCJPqLmEsCIkrk4DL3JvaZH1XA3jy5bKxFlLrDTaf4SWGPXUYrw2yzCrGCpr5cWHcB8Uj3eyvK_0Slws7o23-_z_i6ems7ZlKlrBapk0ENBrRaloQLCyrt37cZ4dyyltFCytIH5uVbqxn82141CLUiCQB_vvFzGr_PIi/Xun2iociFyBE2PR2DsrBc_8mm7Adr0nZ/9"&gt;仅终端订阅者&lt;/a&gt;），这表明在美国历史上并非如此。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3DH9p.CK9aw/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3DH9p.CK9aw/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; Hallmark的分析依赖于一个&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/xCtW0SvRd8whCP7QgKCP08sIH1BdW2sI51Tbm-eJvh0LQZoCihDg9luFnbXjipJTD-Ij4MHTow6CYCbua5s3TKcXeq4k8y3OE-OAzgY2t9sAotJ5hKFqKiZFZw7TPUjBlA9RibncoKKIRiKWrCFEZfw36dtAE-jb7Uwpyvf6J5jrEllRKn4PRp1UJO-tMWL53PQA-W34JSGVuGif2_m2UNnylVB2ybwuCPsgelZvWaH13wZFf61DhPKgMtBggIB3OEJASnKl7a5I7MsgiYyxlJuIlyfH2vvVPVRer6QCTwSzUVINjZrmedT93Mika-zxWeS7RqYXlgVZSI0E8a8yTdK1-lpoNKqCXVUHpiPAKnP9sWXdik8fCT4GLcogJKs1dOkGZFpWM8shUMHXln-PtiZ44vGt8soIGmQ5xc9YpyUOEfEZBhPuoDzX9YU/JlYwu4H0obN_GgoRZ99kxPTCFMytyCf0/9"&gt;名为V-DEM的&lt;/a&gt;政治学数据集的数据，该数据集询问专家“诸如示威，罢工和静坐之类的频繁和大型事件”。他将这些数据与标准普尔500指数的年度GDP增长和增长相比，可以追溯到近一个世纪。这两种经济措施都与抗议数字相关。美国看到更多的政治抗议和大规模动员的几年既不是特别有害或对市场和增长有益。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;在国际上，这个故事大不相同。 IMF的研究将社会动荡与&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/dMEgBa1KglZQfGWcSmTc8nnOXQToL8DwY7HooQ2u14sdq9Im09BCz5mRzE9xyYR7G_IQx59MbonhZ9AFOq4mGRUlh-cu0s6nh4AIufsSsVlTwmOGWpu2iTgUlk9cYJpBwWHHtPI2ibmup_MNXv585g_tskMk5p1YvLW6tq4s_IOGPytWiw20UB7Otp665zKxBGgJakwDyI9e587f6BGG-nJQ01tZxrgsaa30EYAjsxuk8bVZzdJFAhHUHubYh4PwIWuMstWLyyPM38H1VDwGB4Y_8cpwOyoo68hw_yw95c4gyj6oaiSBEJBK7sL37paEJSOD2Mkfxiq10Ax2jVgYDbT9l2BnYvULM9aR_neOcbWa3W5HVz695C-O__9igrghKleO1m74a75qBW1wjRgUDT51LSBwfte34J23pyvxdlXQPyr3IMMHXqDs-FmYZl9TXcCF1xMPll3V9Yx2RG3pW520ywNnVKo3mIawmMp5Xx-7398BJed1Sb6IGMiQyAxnIWm7QQhubPqPZI50wKBJ3roKSK8yiJhiEhdv_zAnHa5MPb6JWmpTGaemLomrbDGz1rTZpvOV6N-_dO6vJzfSjA/lps_UF_1DdJCGf6_Pea_Ml-AKzL1KUTT/9"&gt;降低GDP增长&lt;/a&gt;， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/D2cuXrO178hFehRilrrFTDaF9dSfeRupFfEIruT6cH2eHHvhEcOhnufLSx87XsOpDUhmuGZE3CyxSzKqzyPGwcfLTKll3BHQnFpq3uNCaleHr1JAw3cqjjC_qMTLrBNk9JqikoGkAFpOn8jStwQet3PLVi81X3g8P7VCz4zIF3pUwxmSuCp1ppRBhmoNyNFhWa3knTvBLKSUzHpoOEuzNJ5En_4c6Bm22EZptZ8na_oCJSbbvrHyG-QOuapwFWabtgFHG5uwI3eBjw_reZ425-ySKuMS6M6XPfL7Da-klGHSRuHQxonROXKPxvQ8qcf_yRPi_MWXhwSkI8qR1msdKyHA2SKF-q_6f5tPu6MVa_wzuPy77fIF-uJJdXfAMVSw9w0hpECtVjACSqJQpQ7epxppC2oxmJJadgCvSxCizh7B1tp2GyQsrCXDSzCBYQIexsTgjL1vj9ftGiNRZtZILrQih_PuR-SaojdCWuzkQBiMnbw1nT8U3lwbRaOPkpPi1X-65JBvlB8OBQ7qY3fIO1DVx-_tOn5Q19bUZ_8tOx2nIT5-7hacgq66KvqCw1kWuuFLeQ/FFNN8zYJEiQq8bwwmTdhShYrnWbWVPXs/9"&gt;较低的股票市场回报&lt;/a&gt;和&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/p-P4IktxhB3bf0uK33O4Prz4WOMizGTm-bu1zkO-z-MHz8Nv4p65_BnFmiXITvEtFZ9kKtqon4OHvNtmbiRjVTToUWwOGwIYOCCNjYvniAHGZpytoq9sGgay72iR5mDAz_MS6OtAnEdvcm06caDBWqxIjC9DDvuFtKWHOt-5rcJFCGsRYEKZD4A7V0KNydYAkwGur0CKyhM3nhwNlQkwrworlS-DT6s8SeH-ob1EJY62A_PYX8M0ASuAE2YcknW_Pefa31IsCmjOW1oobqAuk64RLYpM3jnXTURAdM2Np4liHwMMYGNkNKuPO0anMbsnQVIfJ8hgKma2O62UQaBZ4dYQkh6qG8c03ty7LanwsiykFe_DN7r9II6IpRUJ7OFhcXJhlBWvJ_EVF3RJ6e0_3OTZ6lXYGx86I-9BAl_dws97m8wmpstsOQ-6fGFJ-OslqG6Lgkh7xjxLfY4ZoqDd6Zc9y6U5qiqrJPzapcAi1zrkFgeXJt9PuyRBQ43MAzhF0v7J4owH1vSUeV8btP_vHU_vtlgpiBCFQmIAnFmsEaAa8rZausqkmAVgKBSFePD-0dH5dA/0iY_GkYFGRW-R5aapVdH6mfRmmAeKCgT/9"&gt;IPO较弱&lt;/a&gt;联系起来。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;为什么断开连接？在&lt;em&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/H_A9d5GSmv4aac-c9RwiN86wUdUl5e8vQqMrMEJzemxAYI7CfT9rD4kiPkS_X66hIvgRYvok8pMNwutDYacT3NFnLq4Y4yAL_sg-JjUQxf13RCWL72k2eO3jioHoY_WYUvyANBEceca6ZnBbn-_8J3SjlJsnDPkLWxQ_obfTAwHUMvInCH5VCvtr6AwNkmGqDz6QddFqNxXdm2xpRCC6Scqzgm7LP-nwzq1Geiz3EyG5jfjfdcRdGxNDzn1NKYU9mIsF73PFH7dYwmn7AoCL5ltZCgZu7DTXlefIoM4dMQmx0msbd0WZB9rbqPcS61er17mlOmV-S1GvGNJ0lffls-r8lWY095BlBZjO6SnVy3yYJlOfbGxh7p12aWk-acztuO8zoDk57VmGsz-SaLOT9qDVFaMTJx5vm100aK_uur2n0nlXK4zyX9A1uyJty7c1Uczaxl7X4x1n4IcDWrCcmEwdxZAxyde3ZzhV6QfPDHxMjXnwy3puoQVulserPlTGd4hl4B-3sA2boA/M3eGN-YEE2pckmE6AWgRa1EecptfT0YS/9"&gt;震惊，危机和虚假警报&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;中，BCG经济学家Philipp Carlsson-Szlezak和Paul Swartz提供了一种有用的，背对背的方式来思考这个问题。他们在有关地缘政治的一章中提醒读者，“如果地缘政治冲击是影响宏观经济的影响，则必须通过真实，财务和/或机构联系起作用。”换句话说，要产生经济影响，政治动荡必须实际限制供应，需求或贷款，或改变政府的运作方式。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;在最后一点上，国际货币基金组织的研究得出的结论是，动荡转化为较弱的财务绩效的程度取决于研究人员所说的“机构质量”。腐败，更多的政治稳定和安全的法治的国家倾向于吸收抗议和社会动荡，而经济后果却更少。迄今为止，这包括美国。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;em&gt; - 沃尔特·弗里克（Walter Frick），彭博周末&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;预测&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;顾问不再需要制作PowerPoint。&lt;/strong&gt;埃森哲（Accenture）正在使用AI“替换&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Ds0tPzIV2KKxaHnfgV3t_BkHHIGoHm2r-vjdTyq7grUcH5Z0Tf0-sZGJ3GwYAv-XNDZoLgM5N0srdSq34ak7MdJZDVwYPv4iYaf1HeU5z_EJDxMPWkGQ7xBfV4X4kssp321z-trp_IWoF1_fbc7babkGMDPqe-R-9gkcqujA2fAgjANkumntSRCq0UqBVoLe3cLAi8jusSoVbXvSpBo9-8v2tNFq2rMVTF_RV959lmUQCfHRqI1lyH9U8ohvCu-j6s_k2LK-QFwLTD3BkPXUajS8jS7JnFyCVCfvQb5a3shwn5g9_2EOv8Io1kkYAE4NBdldLziXpn2p6ANjigiaWYLFcvnCKILQGbe6CDiPij5JPmlT__UiJxqlBAw/j1AxvPj00WViX8ilKjPOFxqsWoFHo8vy/9"&gt;诸如编译演示文稿之类的死记硬背任务&lt;/a&gt;”，而“麦肯锡公司（McKinsey＆Co。）的顾问越来越多地起草建议，并&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/xR-2vlWAYNLA2VMywwGZnyVrbqHpJFyXLyw5MXaKxQwCEZ-Yxb49EchhUMvlVJWYvt6qeu79LneS1hKl5k4y5lm_vtfg8lA_B_mGsWbvs9P_g7dBrTsMzKzQVGxrhoTMjAfhpLglTeY1tml3iy-H6TzqVcF8WraQ6_5NRDjrkTFa3rexA7ULOxTKaGdgX01XkEQWNRpA9lhqXJSmoI6zz5ZWV1DgAfQE0GtqjL7z-veVv2WUtzroNpXfcGmj5vUQKk1fcteGOjY7JImuEkoUmMy2uA4oxXSUxzDExOi9un3HxlaPS6-trnC9wg8zCDBRKG3hDsKQT0qciOViscmzq73pM-x5xEM2QpkdPtJfit2IUlE3ysdyCd12V0w/2_yJslhfuAopnLtKo6BKUp7640b8wz2k/9"&gt;使用公司的生成人工智能平台制作PowerPoint幻灯片&lt;/a&gt;。”&lt;em&gt; - 梅格·肖特（Meg Short），弗朗辛（Francine Lacqua）和彭博新闻（Bloomberg News）&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;尼古丁小袋将超越帅哥。&lt;/strong&gt; “ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/kFQi_V8N3XOVRvSk0vMhtZioyLhIxKuiAwL2dyWGn2Htn29zMic5caSanEb0MY_govUJ7xQO7t0lCmNi2ZKTr6zsPMvU7l4kMaYFnANOKZ2N0vNpRx2NXs5NQ3xJC1H67V9I8LWpBuc_t8rvO292r5Euj9QwyP7lNScLZKyrNXzlYqVNn7QawEfba4QZfGl-Y8ibpt4mceWT-WypNfEU1878Lw07rYk0nMuZrtRKHrX-wI-ik-YHzmQvG4_SZrqU_eC1U16DMadRbLvuCpz-Aarch8e0w1hLHnpv3TSzzxjf3BvtKaHbsMDvLcPYB22Vx_VAGFEYvnhc54n2OwoF0nDniwmnsfulv792F_PPL3YRi0K-pvnyBpbrP3s/dE94rj8cSVb_syXHMucUaon8TNji9LfS/9"&gt;向女性销售&lt;/a&gt;将有助于初创企业和大型烟草占据蓬勃发展的尼古丁小袋市场的更大份额。”&lt;em&gt; - 乔纳斯·埃克布洛姆（Jonas Ekblom），彭博新闻（Bloomberg News）&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;“流行通货膨胀已经结束。&lt;/strong&gt;请注意，我不是说&amp;#39;通货膨胀已经结束&amp;#39;。在关税和较低的移民之间，可能会&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/7vQ94aB6QVbHMIqtOmCQ95ys2yThxE0EeRgiiS8X-WW67diNGzJI3tMAcNhQMLLWiOPPSW2l_mEiHJjTVNGy0B37APs9sO3xaO5nPvXDERMMGNYs7-bllQZWWwsbSJ2K2ntNxdook7pzpUqZFcDGFPmbt5os5Y97rEKGqcUWEGQS3iT2Qjty2CLRLf_-2N-DQ0ur_-JNgSfR07Rs7CIVsFq2h32p471jz60WBBm7w0wkmp3x1ab7edImNDyDuO-SoedCrJolSWeTyD7g0to5bPjr39ERL6foGkTh9B6bs4RY_fKWTX22r9Yy9eLBUUxXUfJBWkYIYWURkFCb0FoyghofCccTtu95DgDb0jjw3bBeIan7V76iiXR_LPw/TvbyQMcIzSFCBXdeNXSuKpNfqs7J8Psy/9"&gt;稳定在较高但仍可忍受的水平上&lt;/a&gt;。”&lt;em&gt; - 艾莉森·施拉格（Allison Schrager），彭博社的意见&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;美国财政部长斯科特·贝斯特（Scott Bessent）说， &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/m5vWOf3D0uUT6DwDns9ubB4NIMZtOk8Rr4xpAganPeP0kFP8VOmj_dufcLb3s0kFmOA9JIaBNCcGOprlrKKBUtICthHLdpZ-bCb0MpSwysvuNKML16e427z_nwtDbRgBFUoNZpoo-Et9d__4RKuTf7wV6W9GVTxG3nYrp1UmZz6bw2ncNJr6THo5W4aI5nUWyKoS0MwNuM8Zy