bukun，“如果我明天要钱，如果我要销毁房屋，并在混凝土中重建它们。” &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 16px 0px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; border-radius: 8px; padding-bottom: 18px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/2b0cH1vIZVWSEfq7fqOtLhsH48IE93BBqZ2vQiy8ONwejeEsnSVj1glIjU0linEbMOnkPxpH9z2c9cXPdvgJW58zIISv13XHRDGcYz4yUgXrdXYssXvMIRE5-skzTyFj8Enw0_KhmTRgg4zuGsIna2gcj4t23bOMEYW7R9KK56LZNCPZCeATJW-WydsOzM6W6PQ2QQNVjlC_-nV7aiuXVBX3vO8GEuMAV-jPPmm4KASsHY-QoxAbXgAM12ecILhUIHznN1cX55FdWNbw71HZSx_EjqX4wqvm_fNCp89XynuOlyw6_ZhgIWQAtgYxYBPnasMvqr78etXsMiex-ElMTZkoTLqkQKAgJbqBYNPJtYYo6PhyaNKlKHMHwiA/LRCrShHy7jfaYAF-aSSXsIa8IbOJjCAt/9" rel="nofollow" style="color: #000000; text-decoration: none; display: block;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i_0xkUmtTOYE/v1/550x381.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img class="email-ssl-image" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i_0xkUmtTOYE/v1/550x381.jpg" style="border-radius: 8px 8px 0px 0px; width: 550px; height: 381px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/kkzH7Qjdq_B-31B9--ABC7bYdEkFMOred78PcxGJeGwhzUf3pC-ASAcGeVbj6gJ4RH7YCSmxjr-LGvlSd--yR1KOtmDtfke39_4Jb80HafIMtwdY_HJjqM2K0_fVfX69Bm9uwV68qoSywpS_mAlWhi5yiObZZxwiMdFI5jz2LycxTKCdN1d4Po9SXnFjVRCDuxgbDgUHKyK0xiHFa7EnfsvAFvV9BXKEkDVz93O16qAyZ7kHK5LO5l3wniR-QhgOyd9cZ0AjOmUDk8xst_5fJufCaCMGY-ZDDPBRZaHSF8c9y5M6wqfXhX7qmz3Lg_LFZavXHTLEh97