ceNhLmn3PihNk24jM2ckkTx5tv-nP9nXambxgbHlIAGy6VHjVylhUqX8hTJcqm59Xtf3Mu1pLFqlIianMtJTvoWXrCdzJeXuDV_uNd37QQbp4zzcxj6ia4Lyw/ZEGnRcqSiiH7Plr7A-EPp8u3mIUkXwvo/9" target="_blank"&gt;印度航空AI171航班的唯一幸存者&lt;/a&gt;的故事。他坐在第一行经济舱中，设法穿过飞机侧面破的门逃脱。十年来，这次坠机事故在最致命的航空事故中&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/bf4snV8w3TNvZHVr5MMhH7qYs08YUNf27S7DIsjEzaDF-OGNhBnANEPYhdhgzwya1DUdxt0_qXvhXmwFHS-XhmLgaMYs-rdOOjaLCqk0yGB0xwbIIzarS7bBQG2PfSEAq9eWBn1EUV6JHTJ3qTLlwDeYQIcZYs_848Zqp49yoR_kruCjyL3cDx1jroqYbDUy0AZAh4rS5YMWpI1dgse42ahML8XZiR0Q-PCoq443d6YEayEQSFeISXwu2o-DammVncEaRQ5YGLn8b3mOQbwu1CikPw/3EJlhAlXR8uSaVi0hdm5PBoztULo6xV4/9" target="_blank"&gt;杀死了241名乘客&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 16px 0px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 16px 8px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td colspan="2"&gt; Big Take Podcast &lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-bottom-color: #CCC; padding: 16px 8px 9px 0px; border: none;" valign="top" width="129"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/T9NiN2zBanTqyzC3WtzolUoKTJpi0yDR85hYKDIZiR1RARUh0T3pjXuaXWYiLTA_-nXjfv4pKxGR2uRcgdS2eR1DGInK-DAshbbmI7RyN_5ofNCZHgaEBWR08s3qcWLxh7qAxCjDEWDiK3nva6TOrihCERDb4J3gmpCIPz2yfm3Wnl-2PEAj0NyQzITOgX2deieabxs1jqGVUTxmdLGSH0DWrI_Gx1CMSGTxfZUlFaKKnGRzBhJWjexsKh67Omty48R1HZaAhA76qY8RvF0jWll7-w/SPxK9tMWEOPLVIGZUKNJwj2Rd16D-Y4f/9" rel="nofollow" style="color: #000000; text-decoration: none; display: block;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="129"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iRzvvLQr9Veo/v8/129x86.jpg" width="129"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"